    static final Gender
    Gender.fromString(String genderString)
    Simple factory method for determining a gender from a given String, algorithm: if String is null or empty: UNKNOWN if String is "m" or "male": MALE if String is "f" or "female": FEMALE if String is "o" or "other": OTHER if String is "d" or "diverse": DIVERSE if String is "x" or "undefined": UNDEFINED For all other strings it returns UNKNOWN
